<HEAD>Joint Commission Reports on Hitler-Stalin Pact</HEAD>
<BYLINE>RETRANSMITTING a0775 to restore cycle designator ^By DEBORAH G.
SEWARD</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>WARSAW, Poland (AP) </DATELINE>
